##Grab a handful of sunshine

Micro Signal RSZMDFJ

Function introduction, human is the scale of all things, human is the most beautiful scenery.

February 16,2020.

The 23rd day of the 1st Lunar Month.

Day 25 of the siege of Wuhan.

The 24th day the gate of Heaven is sealed.

The sunshine today is good enough to make one forget the snow yesterday. Once turned into water and evaporated by the sun, the once "white-headed" world has been restored to its normal appearance. It's really hard to find solid memories in a world of uncertainty and change. Forgetfulness is human nature, but it is not universal. "Heaven does not give birth to Confucius, for eternity is like the night. " . The reason why we are where we are today depends on the wisdom of the human elite. You know, the baby we have today is no different from the baby we had in the Qin Dynasty. The key is what we, as heirs, should teach them. The Qin people were not "too busy to mourn for themselves" , but rather Burning of books and burying of scholars led to the fall of Kyushu. Later generations are not without "the sad mirror" , Du Mu's "Afanggong Fu" itself is in "the sad mirror" . Every contemporary recorder who gives out his own voice is in the "sad mirror" , but this contemporary sorrow, can only be learned by future generations. The reason why we sigh with Du Mu is because since Qin Dynasty, the high wall is still.

I'm trying really hard to catch a handful of sunshine.

I let go of it. It's empty.

But I knew I had it.
